

LAWIG

   tagal ng panahon, laon, haba ng oras na nagdaraan
   lawig
   long duration

   lumawig
   to prolong

   palawigin
   to extend the time

   patagalin
   to make longer

   pakalawigan
   to take a long time in doing

   mapalawig

   This Tagalog word is not than common in Filipino conversation but
   everyone understands what it means.
